---
const googleMapsUrl = 'https://maps.app.goo.gl/rtoUcQDWsXnkjuTSA';
---

<section class="section section-alt" id="reviews">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">顧客評價</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">睇下其他顧客點講</p>

    <div class="reviews-google">
      <div class="google-badge">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="28" height="28" class="google-icon">
          <path fill="#4285F4" d="M22.56 12.25c0-.78-.07-1.53-.2-2.25H12v4.26h5.92a5.06 5.06 0 0 1-2.2 3.32v2.77h3.57c2.08-1.92 3.28-4.74 3.28-8.1z"/>
          <path fill="#34A853" d="M12 23c2.97 0 5.46-.98 7.28-2.66l-3.57-2.77c-.98.66-2.23 1.06-3.71 1.06-2.86 0-5.29-1.93-6.16-4.53H2.18v2.84C3.99 20.53 7.7 23 12 23z"/>
          <path fill="#FBBC05" d="M5.84 14.09c-.22-.66-.35-1.36-.35-2.09s.13-1.43.35-2.09V7.07H2.18C1.43 8.55 1 10.22 1 12s.43 3.45 1.18 4.93l2.85-2.22.81-.62z"/>
          <path fill="#EA4335" d="M12 5.38c1.62 0 3.06.56 4.21 1.64l3.15-3.15C17.45 2.09 14.97 1 12 1 7.7 1 3.99 3.47 2.18 7.07l3.66 2.84c.87-2.6 3.3-4.53 6.16-4.53z"/>
        </svg>
        <div>
          <strong>Google 評價</strong>
          <div class="google-stars">
            <span class="stars">★★★★★</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href={googleMapsUrl} class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
          onclick="gtag('event','google_review_click',{event_category:'social',event_label:'reviews_badge'})">
          查看所有評價
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="reviews-grid">
      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="review-text">「師傅手工好好，換Mon好快搞掂，價錢公道。推薦！」</p>
        <div class="review-author">— Google 評價用戶</div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="review-text">「iPhone 爆玻璃拎過去，即場整好，服務態度好好。」</p>
        <div class="review-author">— Google 評價用戶</div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="review-text">「換電池好快，而且有保養。深水埗站行幾步就到，好方便。」</p>
        <div class="review-author">— Google 評價用戶</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="reviews-cta">
      <a href={googleMapsUrl} class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
        onclick="gtag('event','google_review_click',{event_category:'social',event_label:'reviews_cta'})">
        📍 喺 Google 查看更多評價
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .reviews-google {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 40px;
  }
  .google-badge {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    background: var(--paper);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 20px 24px;
  }
  .google-icon { flex-shrink: 0; }
  .google-badge strong { font-size: 1rem; }
  .google-stars { margin-top: 2px; }
  .stars { color: #fbbc05; font-size: 1.1rem; letter-spacing: 2px; }
  .google-badge .btn-sm { margin-left: auto; white-space: nowrap; }
  .btn-sm { padding: 8px 20px; font-size: 0.9rem; }

  .reviews-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .review-card {
    background: var(--paper);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 28px 24px;
  }
  .review-stars { color: #fbbc05; font-size: 1.1rem; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .review-text {
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .review-author { color: var(--ink-soft); font-size: 0.85rem; }

  .reviews-cta { text-align: center; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .reviews-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .google-badge { flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .google-badge .btn-sm { margin-left: 0; width: 100%; text-align: center; justify-content: center; }
  }
</style>
